sql.query:
SELECT s.uuid AS student_uuid, s.firstName, s.lastName, SUM(ce.enrolgrandtotal) AS student_total, COUNT(ce.enrolment_uuid) AS enrol_count
FROM students AS s
LEFT JOIN charges_enrolments AS ce ON (ce.student_uuid = s.uuid)
WHERE ce.charge_uuid = :P1 /* {{$_GET.charge_uuid}} */
GROUP BY s.uuid, s.firstName, s.lastName

SELECT DISTINCT ce.enrolment_uuid, cl.startTimeDisplay, cl.classlevel_uuid, cl.instructor_uuid, cl.day
FROM charges_enrolments AS ce
LEFT JOIN classes AS cl ON (cl.uuid = ce.class_uuid)
WHERE ce.student_uuid = :P1 /* {{student_uuid}} */ AND ce.charge_uuid = :P2 /* {{$_GET.charge_uuid}} */

SELECT ce.*, e.dropDate
FROM charges_enrolments AS ce
LEFT JOIN enrolments AS e ON (e.uuid = ce.enrolment_uuid)
WHERE ce.charge_uuid = :P1 /* {{$_GET.charge_uuid}} */ AND ce.enrolment_uuid = :P2 /* {{enrolment_uuid}} */
ORDER BY ce.classDate2 ASC
